{"tid":2478519,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"左報批鬥大館藝術展 醫護抗疫屈「黑暴」 藝發局小組主席痛心：香港玩完","createTime":"2021-04-07T06:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T06:28:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"10a6c1a0e6901e168a0a7ed8a47293612e1ade10","tid":2478519,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:22:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/E7VOVAD5EJDBJOKRPIRUR73UXA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FE7VOVAD5EJDBJOKRPIRUR73UXA%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtFMsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=cd0cb3b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FE7VOVAD5EJDBJOKRPIRUR73UXA%2F&h=316917e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/E7VOVAD5EJDBJOKRPIRUR73UXA/</a><br />\n<br />\n左報批鬥大館藝術展 醫護抗疫屈「黑暴」<br />\n藝發局小組主席痛心：香港玩完<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VdYUVZRM0FWWH4yyv0n56hwrMkk=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PURI7LQDAZEAVI2FSVHNEVL7C4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVdYUVZRM0FWWH4yyv0n56hwrMkk%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPURI7LQDAZEAVI2FSVHNEVL7C4.jpg&h=6ca1a22f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大館展覽「韌生」主題為關注疫境下堅韌不懈的生命，惟一幅以醫護為題材的油畫卻成為左報批鬥對象。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港式的文革在社會不斷擴散，中共喉舌《文匯報》、《大公報》繼早前狙擊西九M+博物館的展覽後，再將矛頭指向另一藝術場地大館。《文匯報》昨報道，指中環大館現正舉辦的一個現代藝術展覽，部份展品有「煽動及縱暴」內容，批評有藝術家企圖美化「黑暴分子」。本港藝術界人士感嘆，藝術創作接連被批鬥，「只能夠話痛心，𠵱家搞創作、策劃、場地管理都會驚，之後索性唔做」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：現場無抗爭書 參觀者不覺煽動<br />\n<br />\n《文匯報》昨日報道稱接獲讀者報料，指大館的賽馬會藝方正舉辦一個現代藝術展覽，有部份展品被指涉及煽動及縱暴內容。報道引述一名「陳先生」指，展覽內容及現場圖書與大館的形象不符合，指大館前身是中區警署，但現時展覽內容與展館形象「格格不入」，「在象徵香港警察的地方，放入涉及黑暴的展品及書籍，令人感覺是存心挑戰，十分反感。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n展覽品包括Pepe蛙<br />\n<br />\n報道並刊登展覽的相片，包括一些遊行人士舉標語、Pepe蛙、以醫護為主題的油畫等；書架上的書籍則包括描述佔中的畫冊等。報道引述工聯會郭偉强批評，展品及圖書內容。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n大館網站顯示，「韌生」是關注疫境中堅韌不懈的生命，由上月21日起至下月2日開放參觀。大館邀請了14位藝術家，各自選擇一名或一組幕後英雄作為創作主題，通過研究或親身採訪，了解這些不圖名利的人物，最終以新的委約作品表達他們近期鮮為人知的處境和經歷。作品涵蓋了醫護人員、機組人員、環保志願者、藝術從業者、人權倡議者等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「係咪頭盔雨傘黃色都禁？」<br />\n<br />\n藝發局視覺藝術小組主。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳錦成不禁反問：「以後係咪頭盔、雨傘、黃色都要禁？如果係咁，玩完㗎啦香港。」他並感嘆「𠵱家（政治）唔知想點樣，搞到咩狀況」，形容「覺得好恐怖」。他認為若將問題噤聲，最終只是等候另一個爆發點。<br />\n<br />\n大館發言人。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4ar_tdxdqu1ME4hdeCqlKPlmQh8=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FHSXONBTVNE4DA2D7PP2J7JEYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4ar_tdxdqu1ME4hdeCqlKPlmQh8%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFHSXONBTVNE4DA2D7PP2J7JEYI.jpg&h=177f9aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「韌生」展期直至下月2日。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VEftehOUdC5OH7uYJzPDjE5KFGI=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZBZECDVZHNBIFK3YM62PPU5OBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVEftehOUdC5OH7uYJzPDjE5KFGI%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZBZECDVZHNBIFK3YM62PPU5OBU.jpg&h=d6456d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■展覽於大館的賽馬會藝方舉行。"},{"pid":"152c9cd098aa165bf7798ade6d9b40af84dd3d91","tid":2478519,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:25:50.000Z","msg":"批鬥開始咗點會完呀<br />\n文革鬥撚足十年去到毛匪落地獄先識停呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7388449c081f339f8b504535198cf472229c7b8b","tid":2478519,"uid":112232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:28:31.000Z","msg":"玩完左好耐啦<br />\n訓左幾多年？"}]}